    "body": "@D4nte \r\nThank you for logging this!\r\nIt is already an open issue https://github.com/status-im/status-react/issues/9763 (it makes confusion around this feature) - basically, now it works this way:\r\n1) if you enable logging with fingerprint - it will log you automatically in case you were logged out automatically (by a timeout or just closing the app)\r\n2) if you logged out from profile and confirmed it - it is considered as manual log out and the app will always ask for keycard in this case\r\ncc @hesterbruikman - maybe we can add new issue / transform existing https://github.com/status-im/status-react/issues/9763 to feature request?\r\n\r\nThis one I believe can be closed, @D4nte reopen if you have more questions.",
